    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The film and media that we create and consume reflects our individual identities, our local and national cultures and the political players on the global stage. Our film and media degree will help you examine these topics using rigorous academic discipline and practical production techniques. Graduates are well equipped for careers in the creative industries and beyond.</p>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
